{"tid":610730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電話App聲稱破解全部Wi-Fi密碼】","createTime":"2018-03-30T08:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T13:29:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9a95e9fbd12a87b76ac95c6504180d253e08ed","tid":610730,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"【央視實測：中銀、外交部如無掩雞籠】<br />\n<br />\n中國近年出現不少電話App，聲稱可以破解全部Wi-Fi密碼。央視記者測試過，發現中銀內部和外交部大樓的Wi-Fi都能輕鬆破解。不過，其實魔鬼在細節，這類程式會收集用戶連接過的Wi-Fi密碼，然後上傳到資料庫，共享給所有人。<br />\n<br />\n意思即是如果你下載了程式，然後連接到家中Wi-Fi，那其他用戶都可以用你家Wi-Fi來上網。如果有人圖謀不軌，對方隨時可以透過Wi-Fi，駭入你的電腦，盜取更多個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#手機App<br />\n#WiFi<br />\n#駭客"},{"pid":"3b090f29dd86872fe41336603430bba06f060900","tid":610730,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1677707062373773/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1677707062373773%2F&d=IpqsRxaBTMs1a32MJNL3jNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a243f0e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1677707062373773/</a>"},{"pid":"38df3584d67f5d2777b88fb066bff447b45365c5","tid":610730,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"雲端共享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be20d5c5153d67365855f5b2c92c2c327f46ca74","tid":610730,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:24:02.000Z","msg":"以前買過隻pc game隨盒附送一個裝置比你駁落wifi，比其他有呢款裝置既人共享wifi ，都差不多十年前"},{"pid":"609299bfc65bd227eb6a0d5981d42296c4ddcd8d","tid":610730,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:26:47.000Z","msg":"邊度有得買？我呼籲d親戚朋友小心d"},{"pid":"8c4c6fbc28ba3a8f5e111fdaaedc7b1674f36f9d","tid":610730,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"609299bfc65bd227eb6a0d5981d42296c4